      { text: `Christopher and Benjamine were in bed when they heard it.\n\nVROOM. VROOM. VROOOOM.\n\nSEVEN MONSTER TRUCKS in the front yard. Wheels taller than Daddy.\n\nRyder on top of the biggest one.\n\n"HEY! YOU TWO! GET DOWN HERE! WE'VE GOT A RACE TO WIN!"\n\nA zip line shot through the window. They grabbed on ‚Äî WHEEEEE! ‚Äî and landed next to Ryder.\n\n"PAW PATROL ‚Äî LET'S ROLL!"\n\nVROOOOOOM!` },
      { text: `All seven trucks launched. The ground shook. Stars blurred.\n\nChase hit the first turn. "Chase is on the case! And on the RACE!"\n\nSkye hit a ramp ‚Äî FLYING. "This pup's gotta fly ‚Äî AND DRIVE!"\n\nZuma hydroplaned sideways. "DUDE! LET'S DIVE IN! WHOAAAA!"\n\nRocky's door fell off. Caught it at full speed. "Don't lose it, reuse it ‚Äî ESPECIALLY AT THIS SPEED!"\n\nMarshall swerved into a cone, a barrel, spun a full circle ‚Äî ended up FIRST.\n\n"HOW DID I DO THAT?!"\n"NO ONE KNOWS!" yelled Chase.` },
      { text: `Dark forest. Trees whooshing past.\n\nBenjamine grabbed Christopher's arm.\n\nThen Rubble's truck lit up like a DISCO BALL. The forest EXPLODED with light.\n\n"RUBBLE ON THE DOUBLE!" Treat in mouth. Teddy bear buckled in.\n\nBenjamine laughed so hard he forgot to be scared.` },
      { text: `"HOLD ON ‚Äî THE BIG JUMP!"\n\nMassive ramp. Pointing at the moon.\n\nAll seven trucks hit it at once.\n\nOne beautiful slow-motion second ‚Äî ALL in the air. Seven monster trucks flying under the stars. Moon RIGHT THERE.\n\n"THIS IS THE BEST NIGHT EVER!"\n\nRyder grinned. "No job is too big ‚Äî no pup is too small ‚Äî and no JUMP is too high!"\n\nBOOM BOOM BOOM ‚Äî they WON.\n\nAll the pups howled. AWOOOOOO!\n\nBenjamine howled too. Tiny and squeaky.` },
      { text: `Trucks drove home slow. Engines purring.\n\nBenjamine leaned against Christopher.\n\n"Can we race tomorrow?" Christopher yawned.\n\n"Every night," said Ryder. "The race starts the second you fall asleep."\n\n"So we have to sleep to race?"\n\n"The fastest way to the race... is to close your eyes."\n\n"Chase is... off the case..."\n"Rubble... on the... snuggle..."\n"I'm good... I'm good..."\n\nTwo brothers smiled, closed their eyes, and raced off into the most amazing dreams.` }
